- Life transitions are major changes that can significantly impact your mental health and overall wellbeing.
- Embracing a strong support system is crucial for navigating the emotional ups and downs of change.
- Whether starting a new job or moving, these periods offer opportunities for personal growth.
- Developing coping strategies like journaling and mindfulness can help [manage stress](https://www.riazcounseling.com/blog-posts/expert-tips-on-how-to-manage-stress-and-anxiety "https://www.riazcounseling.com/blog-posts/expert-tips-on-how-to-manage-stress-and-anxiety") during these times.
